des:
Listen to this story with a timeless lesson. With all this ado about river restoration and building walls, you may wonder, which mad scientist thought of building a wall across a flowing river, in that case you are normal, but for those of us who are 'captive born and raised' and 'head-started', we need this story. I even identify with the little boy Pepe in me, and the fish? They are all around us...
A must add to your bag of stories, we present a timeless tale of a boy and his fish!
At any point, you can say "Alexa, stop" to exit the skill. This skill was created using a Skill Blueprint. Your requests to this skill are not shared with the skill developer.
